title: RL F2P - What has got me worried

media:group.media:title: RL F2P - What has got me worried
media:group.media:description:
Rocket League is going free to play later this summer. Amazing news for everyone you'd think and I agree. So why am I worried? There are some challenges that come from the changes that are about to happen. I really hope Psyonix already has plans for all of these issues in place because it could make the game temporarily worse, if they don't.
